So the blueprint layout should be:
```json
"layout": {
  "rows": [
    [{ "key": "content_items_calendar", "span": 16 }, { "key": "content_items_summary", "span": 8 }]
  ]
}
```

I need to check what prepare-write actually expects since it normalizes the blueprint format, then I'll run the helper with this layout structure and see what happens.

